            "title": "蘋概及手機設備股急彈 瑞聲官宣擬斥12億元回購初段曾飆近23%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">環球關稅戰暫時略為緩解，之前捱沽的蘋果概念與手機設備股今早急彈，其中瑞聲科技(02018)更曾飆22.88%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：瑞聲科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240822_FI_source-web_02018-2.jpeg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：瑞聲科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240822_FI_source-web_02018-2.jpeg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：瑞聲科技官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">瑞聲昨晚發公告，表示去年底落實的1億美元回購計畫已完成，公司昨天決定授權新一輪於未來12至18個月的回購計畫，涉及金額最多12億港元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">換言之，新一輪回購加上之前已完成的回購，涉及金額合共不超過20億港元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">瑞聲科技今早初段一度彈上40.55元，飆22.88%；截至上午約10時21分升幅收窄至13.18%，報37.35元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"舜宇光學官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/02382-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"舜宇光學官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/02382-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">舜宇光學官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">其他蘋概及手機設備股今早亦炒上，比亞迪電子(00285)暫升近11%，舜宇光學(02382)升逾12%，高偉電子(01415)升約13%，丘鈦科技(01478)亦升逾9%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14843391-%e8%98%8b%e6%a6%82%e5%8f%8a%e6%89%8b%e6%a9%9f%e8%a8%ad%e5%82%99%e8%82%a1%e6%80%a5%e5%bd%88-%e7%91%9e%e8%81%b2%e5%ae%98%e5%ae%a3%e6%93%ac%e6%96%a512%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e5%9b%9e%e8%b3%bc%e5%88%9d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240822_FI_source-web_02018-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-10 10:25:50",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
